title: Classic Brownstone, Remodeled; LARGE 2 br w/ Hardwood and Built-Ins!
posting_body: ['This building is located at 2101 Blaisdell Ave S.', 'Great location close to MCAD, U of Mn and all the great shops and restaurant in the area.', 'Get a 1/2 a month FREE with qualifying lease and credit!', 'This is a 2nd floor beautiful apartment', 'We recently update the kitchen with a dishwasher- gas range stove, built in microwave, granite counter tops.', 'There are 2 bedroom, one is HUGE  and one regular size.', 'Beautiful hardwood floors in the living space.', 'The bathroom has cool retro black/ white tiled floor.', 'Plenty of closet space', 'Built in Buffet and high ceilings in the Livingroom.', 'Ready NOW!', 'Check out the photos, they are not of the exact unit but it will give you a feel for the style of the building.', 'New photos coming soon.', 'The actual unit has many more updates.', 'This video is of an upper unit.', '  https://youtu.be/Ucububq3EY4', 'Rent is $1,395', 'Heat, water and trash are included.', 'Ask about off street parking options.', 'Give IrvingProperties a call or email to see this or any of our other properties.', 'show contact info', 'This is a non smoking and no pet building.']
